<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lds&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse &uuml;lesanne </eesti>
<inglise>Purpose of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &uuml;lesandeks on luua Eestis tingimused toimiva konkurentsi tekkimiseks telekommunikatsiooni valdkonnas ja kaitsta tarbijat ebakvaliteetsete kaabelleviteenuste eest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The purpose of this Act is to create conditions for active competition in the telecommunications sector in Estonia and to protect consumers from substandard cable distribution services. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esolev seadus s&auml;testab: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) This Act provides for: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude rajamise tingimused; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the conditions for the construction of cable networks; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude opereerimise tingimused; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the conditions for the operation of cable networks; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanikule ja operaatorile esitatavad n&otilde;uded. </eesti>
<inglise>3) the requirements for owners and operators of cable networks. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabellevi ja kaabelleviv&otilde;rk </eesti>
<inglise>Cable distribution and cable networks </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabellevi k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on televisiooni- v&otilde;i raadiosaadete ja televisiooni- v&otilde;i raadioprogrammide (edaspidi programmid) edastamine abonentidele kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kaudu. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, "cable distribution" means the transmission of television or radio broadcasts and of television or radio programmes (hereinafter programmes) to subscribers through cable networks. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rk k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on tehniliste vahendite s&uuml;steem, mida kasutatakse programmide edastamiseks abonentidele. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, "cable network" means a technical infrastructure used for the transmission of programmes to subscribers. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rk </eesti>
<inglise>Cable television network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rk on territoriaalselt piiritletud kaabelleviv&otilde;rk, mille kaudu v&otilde;etakse vastu ja edastatakse abonentidele maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate ja satelliitide abil v&auml;ljastatud programme ning milles on kaks v&otilde;i enam j&auml;rjestikust: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Cable television network" means a cable network within a defined territory through which programmes emitted by terrestrial broadcasting transmitters or satellites are received and transmitted to subscribers, and which have more than two successive </inglise>
<eesti>1) liiniv&otilde;imendit v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) transmission-line amplifiers; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) liiniv&otilde;imendit-muundajat v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) transmission-line amplifier-converters; or </inglise>
<eesti>3) liiniv&otilde;imendit ja liiniv&otilde;imendit-muundajat. </eesti>
<inglise>3) transmission-line amplifiers and transmission-line amplifier-converters. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu vahendusel riiklikku tegevusluba n&otilde;udva telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutamiseks peab ettev&otilde;tjal olema vastav tegevusluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Undertakings shall have a corresponding activity licence for the provision of telecommunications services requiring a state activity licence through cable television networks. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steem </eesti>
<inglise>Master antenna system </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steem on kaabelleviv&otilde;rk, mille kaudu v&otilde;etakse vastu ja edastatakse abonentidele maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate v&otilde;i satelliitide abil v&auml;ljastatud programme ning milles ei ole j&auml;rjestikuseid: </eesti>
<inglise>"Master antenna system" means a cable network through which programmes emitted by terrestrial broadcasting transmitters or satellites are received and transmitted to subscribers, and which have no successive: </inglise>
<eesti>1) liiniv&otilde;imendeid v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) transmission-line amplifiers; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) liiniv&otilde;imendeid- muundajaid v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) transmission-line amplifier-converters; or </inglise>
<eesti>3) liiniv&otilde;imendeid ja liiniv&otilde;imendeid-muundajaid. </eesti>
<inglise>3) transmission-line amplifiers and transmission-line amplifier-converters. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steem </eesti>
<inglise>Individual reception system </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steem on tehniliste vahendite s&uuml;steem, mille abil isik v&otilde;tab v&otilde;i isikud &uuml;hiselt v&otilde;tavad oma tarbeks vastu programme. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Individual reception system" means a technical infrastructure whereby a person receives or several persons jointly receive programmes for their own use. </inglise>
<eesti>Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi kaudu programmide edastamine abonentidele ei ole lubatud. </eesti>
<inglise>The transmission of programmes to subscribers by individual reception systems is not permitted. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi kasutamine ei v&otilde;i kahjustada programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The use of an individual reception system shall not interfere with the reception or transmission of programmes through other cable networks or by individual reception systems constructed on a legal basis. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaator </eesti>
<inglise>Cable operator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaator on isik, kes edastab kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kaudu abonentidele programme. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Cable operator" means a person who transmits programmes to subscribers through a cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaatoriks v&otilde;ib olla kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanik v&otilde;i omanikuga vastava lepingu s&otilde;lminud ettev&otilde;tja. </eesti>
<inglise>The owner of a cable network or an undertaking which has entered into a corresponding contract with the owner may act as a cable operator. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaator ei v&otilde;i kahjustada programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A cable operator shall not interfere with the reception or transmission of programmes through other cable networks or by individual reception systems constructed on a legal basis. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Abonent </eesti>
<inglise>Subscriber </inglise>
<eesti>Abonent k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga liitunud isik, kellele edastatakse tasu eest programme. </eesti>
<inglise>For the purposes of this Act, "subscriber" means a person connected to a cable network to whom programmes are transmitted for charge. </inglise>
<eesti>Abonendil ei ole &otilde;igust edastada programme kolmandatele isikutele. </eesti>
<inglise>Subscribers have no right to transmit programmes to third persons. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanik </eesti>
<inglise>Owner of cable television network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanikuks v&otilde;ib olla Eestis &auml;riregistrisse kantud ettev&otilde;tja, kellele on k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel v&auml;ljastatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An undertaking entered in the commercial register in Estonia which has been issued a cable television network licence pursuant to this Act may be the owner of a cable television network. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanik ei tohi olla Eestis osutatava k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 11 s&auml;testatud telefoniteenuse k&auml;ibest &uuml;le 40 protsenti omav &auml;ri&uuml;hing v&otilde;i sellise &auml;ri&uuml;hinguga l&auml;bi majandusliku huvi seotud. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The owner of a cable television network shall not be a company which accounts for more than 40 per cent of the turnover in the market of telephone services provided for in &sect; 11 of this Act which are rendered in Estonia; the owner of a cable television network shall have no economic interest in such company. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud majanduslikuks huviks k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses peetakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) For the purposes of this Act, "economic interest" provided for in subsection (2) of this section means: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &uuml;hte kontserni kuulumist v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) belonging to the same group; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i omanike osalist v&otilde;i t&auml;ielikku kattumist otse v&otilde;i l&auml;bi kolmandate isikute v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) if all or some shareholders or owners are the same directly or through third persons; or </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;le 2 protsendi suuruse osaluse omamist teises ettev&otilde;tjas vahetult v&otilde;i l&auml;bi osanike v&otilde;i aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i l&auml;bi kolmandate isikute. </eesti>
<inglise>3) holding in another undertaking directly or through partners, shareholders or third persons, which exceeds 2 per cent. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanikuks olevas ettev&otilde;tjas osalust omavate isikute ring ja nende osalus kolmandates ettev&otilde;tjates peab olema l&auml;bipaistev. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The group of persons with holdings in an undertaking which is the owner of a cable television network, and their holdings in third undertakings shall be transparent. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba </eesti>
<inglise>Cable television network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba on Sideameti poolt v&auml;lja antud tegevusluba, mis annab sellel m&auml;rgitud isikule &otilde;iguse kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu rajamiseks, omamiseks ja kasutamiseks loaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimustel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Cable television network licence" means an activity licence issued by the Communications Board which entitles the person indicated therein to construct, own and use a cable television network under the conditions specified in the licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba antakse v&auml;lja t&auml;htajaga 10 aastat. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Cable television network licences are issued for a term of ten years. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba ei ole edasiantav ning sellest tulenevate &otilde;iguste ja kohustuste t&auml;itmist ei tohi &uuml;le anda k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 8 n&otilde;uetele mittevastavale isikule. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Cable television network licences are not transferable, and compliance with the rights and obligations arising therefrom shall not be transferred to persons who do not meet the requirements of &sect; 8 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabellevi programmide pakett ja p&otilde;hipakett </eesti>
<inglise>Package of programmes distributed by cable and basic package of programmes distributed by cable </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabellevi programmide pakett on kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaatori poolt kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kaudu abonendile edastatavate programmide kogum. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Package of programmes distributed by cable" means a collection of programmes transmitted to subscribers by a cable operator through a cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipakett on kaabellevi programmide pakett, mida kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaator edastab k&otilde;igile abonentidele. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) "Basic package of programmes distributed by cable" means a package of programmes distributed by cable which a cable operator transmits to all subscribers. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>Telekommunikatsiooniteenused </eesti>
<inglise>Telecommunications services </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Telekommunikatsiooniteenus on teenus, mille sisuks on t&auml;ielikult v&otilde;i peamiselt signaalide edastamine telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgus ning &uuml;henduste loomine telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu l&otilde;pp-punktide vahel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Telecommunications services" means services consisting wholly or mainly in the transmission of signals on a telecommunications network, and the creation of connections between the telecommunications network termination points. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Telefoniteenus on telekommunikatsiooniteenus, mis v&otilde;imaldab kasutajale &uuml;henduse telefoniv&otilde;rguga ja k&otilde;ne reaalajas edastamist selle v&otilde;rgu l&otilde;pp-punktide vahel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) "Telephone service" means a telecommunications service which provides users with a connection with a telephone network, and allows the transmission of calls in real time between the termination points of the network. </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu rajamine </eesti>
<inglise>Construction of Cable Network </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu rajamise alused </eesti>
<inglise>Bases for construction of cable television networks </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kohaliku omavalitsuse territooriumile rajatavate kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude piirkonnad m&auml;&auml;rab kindlaks kohaliku omavalitsuse volikogu, piiritledes kogu kohaliku omavalitsuse territooriumi kas &uuml;he kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnana v&otilde;i jagades selle mitmeks kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnaks, v&otilde;ttes aluseks potentsiaalsete abonentide arvu ning l&auml;htudes eesm&auml;rgist tagada kaabellevi kogu omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse territooriumil. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A local government council shall determine the cable television network areas to be constructed within the territory of the local government, and shall designate the entire territory of the local government as one cable television network area, or divide the territory into several cable television network areas based on the number of potential subscribers and with the aim to provide cable distribution services within the entire territory of the local government. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideamet annab igas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas avaliku konkursi alusel v&auml;lja &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitu kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Communications Board shall issue one or several cable television licences for each cable television network area on the basis of a public competition. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideamet annab igas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas avaliku konkursi alusel v&auml;lja &uuml;he kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa, kui m&otilde;ni selle loa taotleja kohustub kogu kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu ulatuses tegevusloa saamisest kaheksa kuu jooksul lisaks programmide edastamisele tagama k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 11 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud teenuse osutamise. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Communications Board shall issue one cable television licence for each cable television network area on the basis of a public competition if any applicant for the licence undertakes, in addition to the transmission of programmes, to provide the service specified in subsection 11 (2) of this Act within the entire scope of the cable television network within eight months after receipt of the activity licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Avalik konkurss kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade v&auml;ljaandmiseks korraldatakse kohaliku omavalitsuse volikogu taotlusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A public competition for the issue of cable television network licences within a cable television network area is organised at the request of a local government council. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotlus peab sisaldama potentsiaalsete abonentide arvu antud piirkonnas ning muid konkursi korraldamiseks vajalikke andmeid. </eesti>
<inglise>The application shall contain the number of potential subscribers in the given area and other data necessary for the organisation of the competition. </inglise>
<eesti>Potentsiaalsete abonentide arvu leidmisel l&auml;htutakse antud piirkonnas asuvate eluruumide ja selles piirkonnas tegutsevate juriidiliste isikute arvust. </eesti>
<inglise>The calculation of the number of potential subscribers shall be based on the number of dwellings located within a given area and on the number of legal persons operating within the area. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi korraldaja </eesti>
<inglise>Organiser of competition </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade konkursi korraldaja on Sideamet. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board is the organiser of a competition for cable television network licences. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Konkursi korraldaja: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The organiser of a competition shall: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kuulutab konkursi v&auml;lja Riigi Teataja Lisas ja v&auml;hemalt &uuml;hes &uuml;leriigilise levikuga p&auml;evalehes mitte hiljem kui kolm kuud enne konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de esitamise t&auml;htaega; </eesti>
<inglise>1) announce the competition in the Riigi Teataja Lisa1 and in at least one national daily newspaper not later than three months prior to the term for submission of competition projects; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;ljastab huvitatud isikutele konkursile registreerumiseks esitatava avalduse, v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml; ja selle osade esitamise vormid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) issue application forms to be filed for registration for the competition and forms for competition projects, and parts thereof to interested persons; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kehtestab konkursile registreerumise t&auml;htaja, mis ei tohi olla l&uuml;hem kui &uuml;ks kuu konkursiteadaande ilmumisest; </eesti>
<inglise>3) establish a term for registration for the competition which shall not be shorter than one month after the publication of the notice of competition; </inglise>
<eesti>4) registreerib konkursil osalejad; </eesti>
<inglise>4) register the participants in the competition; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kehtestab konkursi tingimused ja v&auml;ljastab need huvitatud isikutele; </eesti>
<inglise>5) establish the conditions of the competition and notify interested persons thereof; </inglise>
<eesti>6) vajaduse korral teeb muudatusi konkursi tingimustes, informeerides sellest koheselt k&otilde;iki konkursil osalejaid ning pikendades konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de esitamise t&auml;htaega konkursiteadaande avaldamisest m&ouml;&ouml;dunud aja v&otilde;rra; </eesti>
<inglise>6) if necessary, amend conditions of the competition, promptly notify all participants in the competition thereof and extend the term for submission of competition projects by the period of time elapsed from the publication of the notice of competition; </inglise>
<eesti>7) nimetab v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de hindamiseks moodustatava konkursikomisjoni liikmed; </eesti>
<inglise>7) appoint the members of the competition committee formed for the assessment of competition projects; </inglise>
<eesti>8) nimetab konkursi v&otilde;itja v&otilde;i v&otilde;itjad; </eesti>
<inglise>8) announce the winner or winners of the competition; </inglise>
<eesti>9) avalikustab konkursi tulemused Riigi Teataja Lisas ja v&auml;hemalt &uuml;hes &uuml;leriigilise levikuga p&auml;evalehes ning teatab hiljemalt otsuse tegemise p&auml;evale j&auml;rgneval t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eval igale konkursil osalejale kirjalikult otsusest tema esitatud konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml; kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>9) publish the results of the competition in the Riigi Teataja Lisa and in at least one national daily newspaper, and notify each participant in the competition in writing of the decision concerning the competition project submitted by the participant not later than the working day following the date of making the decision; </inglise>
<eesti>10) v&auml;ljastab konkursi v&otilde;itjale v&otilde;i v&otilde;itjatele kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa &uuml;he kuu jooksul p&auml;rast konkursi tulemuste avalikustamist; </eesti>
<inglise>10) issue a cable television network licence to the winner or winners of the competition within one month after the publication of the competition results; </inglise>
<eesti>11) tagab konkursil osalejate &auml;risaladuse ja esitatud andmete konfidentsiaalsuse. </eesti>
<inglise>11) maintain the confidentiality of business secrets of the participants in the competition and the confidentiality of submitted information. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi tingimused </eesti>
<inglise>Conditions of competition </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Konkursi tingimuste kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisel l&auml;htub Sideamet k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetest ja k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 12 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud taotluses esitatud andmetest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board shall determine the conditions of a competition pursuant to the requirements provided for in this Act and based on the information presented in an application specified in subsection 12 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Konkursi tingimustes peavad sisalduma kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutussev&otilde;tmise t&auml;htajad, kasutusloa saamiseks n&otilde;utavad kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rku iseloomustavad tehnilised parameetrid, kaabellevi programmide pakettide minimaalne arv, kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketti kuuluvate televisiooniprogrammide minimaalne arv, telekommunikatsiooniteenuste loetelu, mille osutamiseks peab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa omanik lisaks programmide edastamisele looma v&otilde;imalused. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The conditions of a competition shall include the conditions for commencement of the exploitation of a cable television network, the technical parameters characterising the cable television network that are required for obtaining a utilisation licence, the minimum number of packages of programmes distributed by cable, the minimum number of television programmes included in the basic package of programmes distributed by cable, the list of telecommunications services for the provision of which the holder of the cable television network licence shall create possibilities in addition to the transmission of programmes. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketti kuuluvate televisiooniprogrammide minimaalse arvu m&auml;&auml;ramisel l&auml;htutakse kuni konkursi korraldamiseni kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas vastuv&otilde;etavate ning teede- ja sideministri kehtestatud tehnilistele n&otilde;uetele vastava signaalitugevusega maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate abil v&auml;ljastatavate programmide arvust. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The minimum number of television programmes included in the basic package of programmes distributed by cable is determined based on the number of programmes which are received within the cable television network area until the organisation of the competition and which are emitted by terrestrial broadcasting transmitters with a signal intensity conforming to the technical requirements established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 15. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 15. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursiteadaanne </eesti>
<inglise>Notice of competition </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursiteadaanne peab sisaldama j&auml;rgmisi andmeid: </eesti>
<inglise>A notice of competition shall include the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkond ja potentsiaalsete abonentide arv selles piirkonnas; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the cable television network area and the number of potential subscribers in the area; </inglise>
<eesti>2) konkursil osalejaks registreerumise t&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the term for registration as participant in the competition; </inglise>
<eesti>3) konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de esitamise t&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the term for submission of competition projects; </inglise>
<eesti>4) konkursi korraldaja aadress ja kontakttelefon. </eesti>
<inglise>4) the address and telephone number of the organiser of the competition. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 16. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 16. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursil osalejate registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of competition participants </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Konkursil osalejaks registreeritakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 8 n&otilde;uetele vastav ettev&otilde;tja, kes on esitanud konkursi korraldajale vormikohase avalduse, millele on lisatud: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Undertakings which comply with the requirements of &sect; 8 of this Act are registered as participants in the competition if they have filed a standard application form, to which the following documents have been appended: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kandeotsus ettev&otilde;tja &auml;riregistrisse kandmise kohta koos registrikaardi &auml;rakirjaga; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a judgment on entry of the undertaking in the commercial register together with a copy of the registry card; </inglise>
<eesti>2) t&auml;ielik teave ettev&otilde;tja aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i osanike kohta ja osaluse kohta teistes ettev&otilde;tjates ning avaldaja kinnitus, et ta vastab k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 8 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele; </eesti>
<inglise>2) full information concerning the shareholders or partners of the undertaking and concerning the holdings of the undertaking in other undertakings, and a confirmation by the applicant that the applicant meets the requirements provided for in &sect; 8 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kviitung riigil&otilde;ivu tasumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>3) a receipt concerning payment of the state fee. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Muudatustest konkursile registreerimisel esitatud andmetes on konkursil osaleja kohustatud konkursi korraldajale teatama k&uuml;mne p&auml;eva jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Participants in a competition are required to notify the organiser of the competition of changes in the information submitted upon registration for the competition within ten days. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Konkursil osalejate &auml;rinimesid ei avalikustata enne konkursile registreerumise t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumist. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The business names of participants in a competition are not disclosed before expiry of the term of registration for the competition. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 17. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 17. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml; </eesti>
<inglise>Competition project </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Konkursil osaleja esitab Sideametile konkursi tingimustega etten&auml;htud vormis konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;, mis peab sisaldama: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Participants in a competition shall submit a competition project to the Communications Board in the form prescribed by the conditions of the competition, which shall contain: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &auml;riplaani koos investeerimisprogrammi ja abonentidele pakutavate telekommunikatsiooniteenuste ning nende hindade &auml;ran&auml;itamisega; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a business plan together with an investment programme, and the telecommunications services offered to the subscribers and the prices thereof; </inglise>
<eesti>2) finantseerimisprogrammi koos tagatiste &auml;ran&auml;itamisega; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a financing plan setting out the security; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu tehnilist eskiisprojekti; </eesti>
<inglise>3) a technical draft project of the cable television network; </inglise>
<eesti>4) ettev&otilde;tja viimase majandusaasta aruannet koos audiitori j&auml;reldusotsusega ning viimase poolaasta bilanssi; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the last annual report of the undertaking together with the audit conclusion, and the balance sheet for the previous six months; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgus edastatavate programmide loetelu kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketi &auml;ran&auml;itamisega; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the list of programmes transmitted via the cable television network, setting out the basic package of programmes distributed by cable; </inglise>
<eesti>6) enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kohalike omavalitsuste korraldatud avalike konkursside tulemuste p&otilde;hjal s&otilde;lmitud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude rajamise lepinguid. </eesti>
<inglise>6) contracts for the construction of cable television networks entered into prior to the entry into force of this Act on the basis of the results of public competitions organised by local governments. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Konkursi korraldaja v&otilde;ib konkursil osalejalt n&otilde;uda t&auml;iendavate dokumentide esitamist konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;s sisalduvate andmete t&auml;psustamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The organiser of a competition may require that participants in the competition submit additional documents to specify the information contained in the competition projects. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) T&auml;iendavate dokumentide n&otilde;udmine ei v&otilde;i kitsendada &uuml;hegi konkursist osav&otilde;tja v&otilde;rdse konkureerimise &otilde;igust. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The requirement for submission of additional documents shall not restrict the right of equal competition of any participant in the competition. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;d konkursil osalejale ei tagastata ja tema n&otilde;usolekuta ei avalikustata. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Competition projects are not returned to the participants in the competition, and shall not be made public without the consent of the participants. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 18. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 18. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de hindamine </eesti>
<inglise>Assessment of competition projects </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 13 l&otilde;ike 2 punktis 7 nimetatud konkursikomisjon hindab konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de vastavust konkursi tingimustele, sealhulgas konkurentsiv&otilde;imet telekommunikatsiooniteenuste osutamisel ning tarbijate huvide arvestamist, investeerimisprogrammi usaldusv&auml;&auml;rsust ja kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu tehnilise eskiisprojekti taset ning valib v&auml;lja ja esitab Sideametile kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa v&auml;ljastamiseks parima v&otilde;i parimad v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;d. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The competition committee specified in clause 13 (2) 7) of this Act shall assess the compliance of competition projects with the conditions of the competition, including competitiveness in the provision of telecommunications services, consideration of the interests of consumers, the reliability of the investment programme and the level of the technical draft project of the cable television network, and shall select and submit the best competition project or projects to the Communications Board for the issue of a cable television network licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&otilde;rdsete v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de puhul k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 12 l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatud juhul l&auml;htub konkursikomisjon parima v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml; valimisel kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa taotleja v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;s esitatud telekommunikatsiooniteenuste mahust ja kvaliteedist ning varem &sect; 40 alusel v&auml;lja antud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa olemasolust. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the competition committee considers several competition projects to be of equal value in the case provided for in subsection 12 (3) of this Act, the competition committee shall select the best competition project on the basis of the volume and quality of telecommunications services presented in the competition projects by the applicants for a cable television network licence and the existence of a cable television network licence issued earlier pursuant to &sect; 40 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideameti peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja teeb konkursikomisjoni soovitusel otsuse konkursi tulemuste kohta nelja kuu jooksul p&auml;rast v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de esitamise t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Director General of the Communications Board or his or her deputy shall make a decision concerning the competition results on the recommendation of the competition committee within four months after the term for submission of competition projects. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 19. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 19. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi eba&otilde;nnestumine </eesti>
<inglise>Failure of competition </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Konkurss kuulutatakse eba&otilde;nnestunuks, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A competition is declared to have failed if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) konkursile ei registreeritud &uuml;htegi k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetele vastavat osalejat; </eesti>
<inglise>1) no participant meeting the requirements of this Act were registered for the competition; </inglise>
<eesti>2) &uuml;kski konkursile esitatud v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml; ei vastanud konkursi tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise>2) no competition project complied with the conditions of the competition. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kuue kuu jooksul esimese konkursi eba&otilde;nnestunuks kuulutamisest korraldab Sideamet uue konkursi samas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade v&auml;ljaandmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Within six months after the first competition is declared to have failed, the Communications Board shall organise a new competition for the issue of cable television network licences in the same cable television network area. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 20. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 20. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loaga m&auml;&auml;ratavad tingimused </eesti>
<inglise>Conditions determined by cable television network licence </inglise>
<eesti>L&auml;htuvalt konkursi tingimustest ja konkursi v&otilde;itnud isiku v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;s esitatud andmetest m&auml;&auml;ratakse kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loaga kindlaks kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i selle osade kasutussev&otilde;tmise t&auml;htajad, kasutusloa saamiseks n&otilde;utavad kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rku iseloomustavad tehnilised parameetrid, kaabelleviprogrammide pakettide minimaalne arv, kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketti kuuluvate programmide minimaalne arv ning telekommunikatsiooniteenuste t&auml;htajad ja loetelu, mille osutamiseks lisaks programmide edastamisele peab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa omanik looma vastavad v&otilde;imalused ning muud olulised tingimused. </eesti>
<inglise>Based on the conditions of a competition and the information presented in the competition project of the person who won the competition, a cable television network licence shall set out the conditions for commencement of the exploitation of the cable television network or parts thereof, the technical parameters characterising the cable television network required for obtaining a utilisation licence, the minimum number of packages of programmes distributed by cable, the minimum number of programmes contained in the basic package of programmes distributed by cable and the terms and list of telecommunications services for the provision of which the holder of the cable television network licence shall create appropriate conditions in addition to the transmission of programmes, and other conditions. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 21. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 21. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu rajamise ja opereerimise &uuml;le </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision over construction and operation of cable television network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalvet kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu rajamise ja opereerimise &uuml;le teostab Sideamet seaduse alusel ning teede- ja sideministri kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board shall exercise supervision over the construction and operation of cable television networks pursuant to law and pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalve teostamise k&auml;igus Sideamet: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In the process of exercising supervision, the Communications Board shall: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kontrollib kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu ehitusprojekti vastavust kehtivatele &otilde;igusaktidele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) monitor the compliance of the building design documentation of cable television networks with the legislation in force; </inglise>
<eesti>2) korraldab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu ehitusprojekti ekspertiisi vastavalt vajadusele; </eesti>
<inglise>2) organise the expert assessment of the building design documentation of cable television networks as required; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kontrollib kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu vastavust &otilde;igusaktidega kehtestatud tehnilistele n&otilde;uetele; </eesti>
<inglise>3) monitor the compatibility of cable television networks with the technical requirements established by legislation; </inglise>
<eesti>4) v&auml;ljastab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusloa; </eesti>
<inglise>4) issue cable television network utilisation licences; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kontrollib kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimist ja korrashoidu. </eesti>
<inglise>5) monitor the operation and maintenance of cable television networks. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideameti peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja teeb kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa tingimuste rikkumise korral kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa omanikule ettekirjutuse rikkumise k&otilde;rvaldamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the event of a violation of the conditions of a cable television network licence, the Director General of the Communications Board or his or her deputy shall issue a precept to the holder of the cable television network licence for the elimination of the violation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 22. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 22. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa kehtetuks tunnistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Revocation of cable television network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Sideameti peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja tunnistab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa kehtetuks, kui loale m&auml;rgitud isik: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Director General of the Communications Board or his or her deputy shall revoke a cable television network licence if the person indicated in the licence: </inglise>
<eesti>1) esitab sellekohase taotluse v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) submits an application to this effect; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) ei t&auml;ida kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimusi v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) fails to comply with the conditions set out in the cable television network licence; or </inglise>
<eesti>3) ei t&auml;ida oma tegevuses k&auml;esolevast seadusest tulenevaid n&otilde;udeid v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>3) fails to comply with the requirements arising from this Act in the person's activity; or </inglise>
<eesti>4) esitas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade konkursile valeandmeid v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>4) submitted false information for a competition for cable television network licences; or </inglise>
<eesti>5) ei oma kehtivaid lepinguid programmide edastamiseks kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgus edastatavate programmide levitamise &otilde;igusi omavate isikutega v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>5) lacks valid contracts for the transmission of programmes with persons holding the right to distribute programmes transmitted via cable television network; or </inglise>
<eesti>6) kahjustab oma tegevuse v&otilde;i tegevusetusega samas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>6) prejudices, by act or omission, the reception or transmission of programmes within the same cable television network area through other cable networks or by individual receptions systems constructed on a legal basis; or </inglise>
<eesti>7) on pankrotistunud v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>7) is bankrupt; or </inglise>
<eesti>8) ei vasta k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 8 n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>8) does not meet the requirements of &sect; 8 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideameti peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja tunnistab tema tehtud ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise korral kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa kehtetuks motiveeritud k&auml;skkirjaga, milles on &auml;ra n&auml;idatud loa kehtetuks tunnistamise &otilde;iguslik alus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Director General of the Communications Board or his or her deputy shall revoke a cable television network licence upon failure to comply with the precept issued by him or her with a reasoned directive, which shall set out the legal basis for the revocation of the licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud k&auml;skkirja &auml;rakiri v&auml;ljastatakse kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa omanikule ja vastava kohaliku omavalitsuse volikogule. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A copy of the directive specified in subsection (2) of this section shall be issued to the holder of the cable television network licence and the corresponding local government council. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 23. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 23. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi korraldamine p&auml;rast kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa kehtetuks tunnistamist </eesti>
<inglise>Organisation of competition after revocation of cable television network licence </inglise>
<eesti>Kui kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonna kohta v&auml;ljastatud tegevuslubadest viimane on tunnistatud kehtetuks aasta jooksul p&auml;rast selle v&auml;ljastamist, kuulutab Sideamet kahe kuu jooksul v&auml;lja konkursi samas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade v&auml;ljaandmiseks k&auml;esoleva seadusega s&auml;testatud korras ja endistel tingimustel, kui kohaliku omavalitsuse volikogu ei taotle k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 12 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud taotluse andmete muutmist. </eesti>
<inglise>If the last activity licence for a cable television network area is revoked within a year after the issue thereof, the Communications Board shall announce a competition for the issue of cable television network licences within the same cable television network area within two months pursuant to the procedure provided for in this Act and under the former conditions, unless the local government council applies for the alteration of the information of the application specified in subsection 12 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkursi korraldamine kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumisel </eesti>
<inglise>Organisation of competition upon expiry of cable television network licence </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;hemalt kaheksa kuud enne kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumist kuulutab Sideamet v&auml;lja konkursi samas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade v&auml;ljaandmiseks k&auml;esoleva seadusega s&auml;testatud korras, kusjuures ei rakendata k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 12 l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatut. </eesti>
<inglise>At least eight months before the expiry of a cable television network licence, the Communications Board shall announce a competition for the issue of cable television network licences in the same cable television network area pursuant to the procedure provided for in this Act, whereas the provisions of subsection 12 (3) of this Act are not applied. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehniline &uuml;levaatus </eesti>
<inglise>Technical inspection of cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rk peab l&auml;bima kasutusk&otilde;lblikkuse kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks kohustusliku tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse teede- ja sideministri kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order to assess the fitness for use of a cable television network, it shall undergo a mandatory technical inspection pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse v&otilde;ib l&auml;bi viia &uuml;ksnes vastavat tegevusluba omav ettev&otilde;tja. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The technical inspection of cable networks may be conducted only by undertakings holding an appropriate activity licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse tegevusluba taotleval ja omaval ettev&otilde;tjal peab olema selleks tegevuseks vajalik tehniline varustus ja ta peab kindlustama &uuml;levaatuse teostamise vastava ala asjatundjate poolt. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Undertakings applying for or holding an activity licence for the technical inspection of cable networks shall have necessary equipment for such activity and ensure that technical inspections are carried out by experts in the field. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse teostanud ettev&otilde;tja peab tagama tema poolt esitatavate andmete &otilde;igsuse. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Undertakings which have carried out a technical inspection of cable networks shall ensure the correctness of data that they present. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse tegevuslubasid v&auml;ljastab ja tunnistab kehtetuks teede- ja sideminister k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel ja Vabariigi Valitsuse kinnitatud korra kohaselt. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Activity licences for the technical inspection of cable networks shall be issued and revoked by the Minister of Transport and Communications pursuant to this Act and pursuant to the procedure approved by the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse tegevusloa kehtivuse t&auml;htaeg on kolm aastat. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The term of activity licences for the technical inspection of cable networks is three years. </inglise>
<eesti>Teede- ja sideministril on &otilde;igus l&otilde;petada tegevusloa kehtivus ennet&auml;htaegselt j&auml;rgmistel juhtudel: </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of Transport and Communications has the right to prematurely terminate activity licences in the following cases: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ettev&otilde;tja ei vasta k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) an undertaking does not meet the requirements provided for in subsection (3) of this section; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) ettev&otilde;tja on esitanud tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse l&auml;biviimise tulemuste kohta eba&otilde;igeid andmeid v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) an undertaking has submitted inaccurate information concerning the results of the conduct of technical inspection; or </inglise>
<eesti>3) ettev&otilde;tja taotlusel. </eesti>
<inglise>3) at the request of an undertaking. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Tegevusloa kehtivuse l&otilde;ppemisel k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 6 punktide 1 ja 2 alusel ei saa ettev&otilde;tjale uut tegevusluba v&auml;ljastada enne &uuml;he aasta m&ouml;&ouml;dumist tegevusloa kehtetuks tunnistamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) Upon the expiry of an activity licence pursuant to clauses (6) 1) or 2) of this section, a new activity licence shall not be issued to the undertaking before one year has passed after the revocation of the licence. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 26. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 26. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusluba </eesti>
<inglise>Cable television network utilisation licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusluba on luba, mille Sideamet annab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa alusel projekti kohaselt rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgule. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Cable television network utilisation licence" means a licence that is issued by the Communications Board for a cable television network constructed on the basis of a cable television network licence according to a design. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgule antakse kasutusluba teede- ja sideministri kehtestatud korras p&auml;rast tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse l&auml;bimist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A cable television network is issued a utilisation licence pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Transport and Communications after the cable television network has undergone technical inspection. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rku v&otilde;ib kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimuste kohasele opereerimisele anda p&auml;rast kasutusloa saamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A cable television network may be put into operation according to the conditions determined by the cable television network licence after the receipt of a utilisation licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kasutusloa v&otilde;ib v&auml;ljastada kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgule tervikuna v&otilde;i selle osale. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A utilisation licence may be issued for a whole cable television network or for a part thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimine ilma kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusloata on keelatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The operation of a cable television network without a cable television network utilisation licence is prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 27. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 27. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutusload </eesti>
<inglise>Master antenna system utilisation licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutusluba on luba, mille Sideamet annab projekti kohaselt rajatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemile. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Master antenna system utilisation licence" means a licence that is issued by the Communication Board for a master antenna system constructed according to a design. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemile antakse kasutusluba teede- ja sideministri kehtestatud korras p&auml;rast tehnilise &uuml;levaatuse l&auml;bimist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A utilisation licence is issued for a master antenna system pursuant to the procedure established by the Minister of Transport and Communications after the master antenna system has undergone technical inspection. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi opereerimine ilma kasutusloata on keelatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The operation of a master antenna system without a utilisation licence is prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>3. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 3 </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu opereerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Operation of Cable Network </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 28. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 28. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimise kohustuslikud tingimused </eesti>
<inglise>Mandatory conditions for operation of cable television network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa omanik peab tagama j&auml;rgmiste programmide edastamise kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketis: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a cable television network shall ensure the transmission of the following programmes within the basic package of programmes distributed by cable: </inglise>
<eesti>1) Eesti avalik-&otilde;iguslike ringh&auml;&auml;lingujaamade programmid; </eesti>
<inglise>1) programmes of Estonian public law broadcasting stations; </inglise>
<eesti>2) maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate poolt edastatavad kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas tehnilistele n&otilde;uetele vastava signaalitugevuse juures vastuv&otilde;etavad televisiooniprogrammid, mille edastamise eest omanik ei n&otilde;ua tasu. </eesti>
<inglise>2) television programmes transmitted by terrestrial broadcasting transmitters within a cable television network area that are received at a signal intensity compatible with the technical requirements and for the transmission of which the owner requires no charge. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Enda loodud programmide edastamiseks peab kaabellevi operaatoril olema ringh&auml;&auml;linguseaduses (RT I 1994, 42, 680; 66, 1145; 1995, 83, 1437; 97, 1664; 1996, 49, 953; 1997, 29, 448; 52, 834; 93, 1564; 1998, 2, 42 ja 44; 1999, 16, 268) s&auml;testatud ringh&auml;&auml;linguluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) To transmit its own programmes, a cable operator shall hold a broadcasting licence provided for in the Broadcasting Act (RT I 1994, 42, 680; 66, 1145; 1995, 83, 1437; 97, 1664; 1996, 49, 953; 1997, 29, 448; 52, 834; 93, 1564; 1998, 2, 42 and 44; 1999, 16, 268). </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideameti n&otilde;udmisel on kaabellevi operaator kohustatud esitama tema edastatud programmide salvestuse, kui see n&otilde;ue on esitatud 20 p&auml;eva jooksul programmi edastamisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) At the request of the Communications Board, a cable operator is required to submit recordings of programmes transmitted by the cable operator if such requirement is made within twenty days after the transmission of the programmes. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabellevi operaator on kohustatud programmide edastamisel v&otilde;i taasedastamisel j&auml;rgima autori&otilde;iguse kaitsega seonduvaid n&otilde;udeid ning s&otilde;lmima lepingud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgus edastatavate programmide levitamise &otilde;igusi omavate isikutega. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Cable operators are required to adhere to the requirements relating to copyright protection in the transmission or retransmission of programmes and enter into contracts with persons holding the right to distribute programmes transmitted via cable television network. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 29. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 29. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu vaba mahu opereerimisele andmine </eesti>
<inglise>Using spare capacity of cable television network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanik on kohustatud andma kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu vaba mahu, mis ei ole h&otilde;ivatud v&otilde;i mille h&otilde;ivamist ei ole ette n&auml;htud l&auml;hema &uuml;he aasta jooksul ja milleks ei ole koostatud vastavat projekti v&otilde;i s&otilde;lmitud lepingut, opereerimisele koosk&otilde;las konkurentsiseaduse (RT I 1998, 30, 410) &sect;-ga 18. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The owner of a cable television network is required to grant for use, in accordance with &sect; 18 of the Competition Act (RT I 1998, 30, 410), the spare capacity of the cable television network which is not used or the use of which is not foreseen within the next year, and for which no appropriate project has been prepared or no contract has been entered into. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui olemasolevas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgus vaba maht puudub, kuulutab Sideamet kohaliku omavalitsuse volikogu taotlusel v&auml;lja t&auml;iendava kaabeltelevisioonilubade konkursi, millega ei kaasne luba telekommunikatsiooniteenuste osutamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the existing cable television network has no spare capacity, the Communications Board shall declare an additional competition for cable television network licences at the request of a local government council which does not result in the issue of licences for the provision of telecommunications services. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 30. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 30. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi opereerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Operation of master antenna system </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi opereerimine toimub k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 28 s&auml;testatud tingimustel. </eesti>
<inglise>Master antenna systems are operated under the conditions provided for in &sect; 28 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 31. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 31. </inglise>
<eesti>Liitumine kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga </eesti>
<inglise>Connection to cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Abonendi liitumisel kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga s&otilde;lmitakse tema ja kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu operaatori vahel kirjalik leping, mis peab s&auml;testama poolte vastastikused &otilde;igused ja kohustused, sealhulgas: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Upon the connection of a subscriber to a cable network, a written contract is entered into between the subscriber and the cable operator, which shall provide for the mutual rights and obligations of the parties, including: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga liitumise viisi, t&auml;htaja ja selle eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the manner of and the term and charge for connection to the cable network; </inglise>
<eesti>2) &uuml;henduse korrashoiu ja selle eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>2) connection maintenance and charge therefor; </inglise>
<eesti>3) edastatavate programmide arvu, nimetused ja paketeerituse; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the number and titles of transmitted programmes, and the composition of the package of programmes; </inglise>
<eesti>4) programmisignaali tehnilise kvaliteedi; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the technical quality of programme signals; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kasutamiseks lubatud vastuv&otilde;tjate liigid ja arvu; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the types and number of receivers the use of which is permitted; </inglise>
<eesti>6) programmisignaali kasutamise eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the charge for the use of programme signals; </inglise>
<eesti>7) lepingu muutmise ja t&auml;iendamise korra ning poolte vastutuse. </eesti>
<inglise>7) the procedure for amendment of the contract and the liability of the parties. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omandi&otilde;iguse &uuml;leminekul teisele isikule j&auml;&auml;b k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud kehtiv leping j&otilde;usse ka uue omaniku suhtes, kui kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu uus omanik ja abonent ei lepi kokku teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon the transfer of the right of ownership in a cable network from one person to another, the contract specified in subsection (1) of this section shall remain in force with regard to the new owner, unless the new owner and subscriber agree otherwise. </inglise>
<eesti>4. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 4 </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve ja vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision and Liability </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve seaduse t&auml;itmise &uuml;le </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision over compliance with law </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalvet k&auml;esoleva seaduse ja sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide t&auml;itmise &uuml;le teostab Sideamet. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Supervision over compliance with this Act and legislation arising therefrom shall be exercised by the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalvet teostavad ametnikud k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on Sideameti peadirektor ja tema aset&auml;itja ning nende poolt j&auml;relevalve teostamiseks volitatud ametnikud (edaspidi ametnikud). </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, "officials exercising supervision" means the Director General of the Communications Board, his or her deputy and the officials authorised to exercise supervision by them (hereinafter officials). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 33. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 33. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutus </eesti>
<inglise>Precept </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalvet teostaval ametnikul on &otilde;igus teha kaabelleviv&otilde;rku omavatele v&otilde;i opereerivatele ettev&otilde;tjatele kohustuslikke ettekirjutusi &otilde;iguserikkumise l&otilde;petamiseks v&otilde;i teatud toimingute sooritamiseks v&otilde;i tegevuse peatamiseks, kui kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu rajamise, kasutusseandmise v&otilde;i opereerimise kontrollimisel on avastatud k&auml;esoleva seaduse, muude &otilde;igusaktide v&otilde;i kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loaga s&auml;testatud tingimuste rikkumisi. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An official exercising supervision has the right to issue mandatory precepts to undertakings which own or operate cable networks for the termination of an offence, for the performance of particular activities or for the suspension of activities if violations of the conditions provided for in this Act, other legislation or a cable television network licence are detected upon the monitoring of the construction, putting into operation or the operation of a cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutuses peab sisalduma: </eesti>
<inglise>The precept shall contain: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ettekirjutuse koostanud ametniku nimi ja ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name and position of the official who prepared the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>2) ettekirjutuse tegemise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the date of issue of the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kaabelleviv&otilde;rku omava v&otilde;i opereeriva ettev&otilde;tja &auml;rinimi v&otilde;i nimi; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the business name or name of the undertaking which owns or operates the cable network; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu piirkond; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the cable network area; </inglise>
<eesti>5) ettekirjutuse tegemise &otilde;iguslikud alused ja ettekirjutuse tegemist tingivad asjaolud; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the legal bases for issue of the precept, and the circumstances underlying the issue of the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>6) ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmise t&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the term for compliance with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>7) viide ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmisel rakendatavatele sanktsioonidele. </eesti>
<inglise>7) a reference to the sanctions to be applied in the case of failure to comply with the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ettekirjutus antakse ettev&otilde;tjale v&otilde;i tema esindajale k&auml;tte vahetult allkirja vastu v&otilde;i saadetakse posti teel v&auml;ljastusteatega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The precept shall be delivered directly to the undertaking or representative of the undertaking against signature, or shall be delivered by post with a notice of delivery. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omaniku ja operaatori tegevuse kontrollimine </eesti>
<inglise>Monitoring of activities of owner and operator of cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmise kontrollimiseks on j&auml;relevalvet teostaval ametnikul &otilde;igus kontrollida kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu tehnilist seisundit ning kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omaniku ja operaatori majandustegevust kajastavaid dokumente ning teha dokumentidest v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid ja &auml;rakirju. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) To monitor compliance with the requirements of this Act, an official exercising supervision has the right to inspect the technical conditions of cable networks, and the documents concerning the business activity of owners or operators of cable networks, and to make extracts from and copies of such documents. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalvet teostav ametnik on kohustatud hoidma kontrollimise k&auml;igus talle teatavaks saanud ettev&otilde;tja &auml;risaladust ning kasutama saadud teavet ainult j&auml;relevalve teostamisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An official exercising supervision is required to maintain the business secrets of undertakings which become known to him or her in the course of monitoring, and to use obtained information only in the exercise of supervision. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 35. </inglise>
<eesti>Teabe andmise kohustus </eesti>
<inglise>Duty to provide information </inglise>
<eesti>Sideameti n&otilde;udel on kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanik, operaator v&otilde;i nende esindaja kohustatud: </eesti>
<inglise>At the request of the Communications Board, the owner or operator of a cable network or a representative thereof is required to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ilmuma Sideametisse selgituste andmiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>1) appear at the Communications Board to provide explanations; </inglise>
<eesti>2) esitama Sideametile tema valduses olevaid tehnilisi projekte, abonentlepinguid ja muid dokumente, mis puudutavad kaabelleviga seotud tegevust; 3) v&otilde;imaldama j&auml;relevalvet teostavale ametnikule juurdep&auml;&auml;su kaabelleviv&otilde;rgule. </eesti>
<inglise>2) submit to the Communications Board technical designs, subscriber contracts and other documents in the possession of the owner or operator of the cable network or representative thereof which pertain to the activities related to cable distribution; 3) grant an official exercising supervision access to the cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 36. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 36. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omaniku ja operaatori haldusvastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability of owner and operator of cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Juriidilisest isikust ettev&otilde;tja vastutab k&auml;esoleva seaduse rikkumise korral k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 37 alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An undertaking which is a legal person is liable for a violation of this Act pursuant to &sect; 37 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) F&uuml;&uuml;silise isiku vastutus s&auml;testatakse haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1997, 66-68, 1109; 73, 1201; 81, 1361 ja 1362; 86, 1459 ja 1461; 87, 1466 ja 1467; 93, 1561, 1563-1565; 1998, 2, 42; 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 410; 34, 484; 36/37, 552 ja 553; 38, 562; 51, 756 ja 759; 52/53, 771; 60, 951 ja 952; 64/65, 1004; 86/87, 1409; 98/99, 1574; 103, 1695; 108/109, 1783; 1999, 4, 53; 10, 149 ja 156; 16, 267, 271, 272, 276). </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The liability of natural persons is provided for in the Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1997, 66-68, 1109; 73, 1201; 81, 1361 and 1362; 86, 1459 and 1461; 87, 1466 and 1467; 93, 1561, 1563-1565; 1998, 2, 42; 17, 265; 23, 321; 30, 410; 34, 484; 36/37, 552 and 553; 38, 562; 51, 756 and 759; 52/53, 771; 60, 951 and 952; 64/65, 1004; 86/87, 1409; 98/99, 1574; 103, 1695; 108/109, 1783; 1999, 4, 53; 10, 149 and 156; 16, 267, 271, 272, 276). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 37. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 37. </inglise>
<eesti>Juriidilise isiku vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Liability of legal person </inglise>
<eesti>Juriidilistele isikutele kohaldatakse haldusvastutust j&auml;rgmiste &otilde;iguserikkumiste korral: </eesti>
<inglise>A legal person shall bear administrative liability for the following offences: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ilma k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 9 s&auml;testatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loata kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimise v&otilde;i opereerimisele andmise eest, kui sama tegevuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 100 000 kuni 1 000 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a fine between 100 000 and 1 000 000 kroons is imposed for the operation of a cable television network or for the grant of a cable television network for operation without a cable television network licence provided for in &sect; 9 of this Act if a precept has been issued for the termination of such activity, and the person has failed to comply with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i selle osa opereerimisele andmise eest ilma k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 26 s&auml;testatud kasutusloata, kui sama tegevuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 20 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a fine of up to 20 000 kroons is imposed for the grant of a cable television network or a part thereof for operation without a utilisation licence provided for in &sect; 26 of this Act, if a precept has been issued for the termination of such activity and the person has failed to comply with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi opereerimise eest ilma k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 27 s&auml;testatud kasutusloata, kui sama tegevuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 10 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) a fine of up to 10 000 kroons is imposed for the operation of a master antenna system without a utilisation licence provided for in &sect; 27 of this Act, if a precept has been issued for the termination of such activity and the person has failed to comply with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omaniku poolt k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 20 alusel s&auml;testatud tingimuste t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise eest, kui sama teo v&otilde;i tegevusetuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 100 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>4) a fine of up to 100 000 kroons is imposed for failure by the owner of a cable television network to comply with the conditions provided for in &sect; 20 of this Act, if a precept has been issued for the termination of such activity or omission, and the person has failed to comply with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>5) k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi punktides 1-4 nimetamata k&auml;esolevast seadusest tulenevate n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest, kui sama teo v&otilde;i tegevusetuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 10 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>5) a fine of up to 10 000 kroons is imposed for a violation of the requirements arising from this Act which are not specified in clauses 1) -4) of this section, if a precept has been issued for the termination of such act or omission and the person has failed to comply with the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 38. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 38. </inglise>
<eesti>Protokolli koostamine </eesti>
<inglise>Preparation of report </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 37 loetletud juriidilise isiku haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste kohta protokolli koostamise &otilde;igus on j&auml;relevalvet teostaval ametnikul. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An official exercising supervision has the right to prepare a report on administrative offences of legal persons set out in &sect; 37 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Protokollis tuuakse &auml;ra selle koostamise aeg ja koht, protokolli koostanud isiku ametinimetus ning ees- ja perekonnanimi, haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja &auml;rinimi ja aadress (haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja ees- ja perekonnanimi ning ametikoht), haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise kirjeldus, viide k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 37 s&auml;ttele, mis n&auml;eb ette vastutuse selle haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise eest, haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja seletus ja muud andmed, mis on vajalikud asja lahendamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>The report shall set out the date and place of preparation thereof, the official title, given name and surname of the person who prepared the report, the business name and address of the administrative offender (given name and surname and position of the representative of the administrative offender), description of the administrative offence, reference to the provision of &sect; 37 of this Act which prescribes liability for such administrative offence, the explanation of the representative of the administrative offender, and other information necessary for adjudication of the matter. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Protokollile kirjutavad alla selle koostanud isik ja haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The report shall be signed by the person who prepared it and the representative of the administrative offender. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja keeldub protokollile alla kirjutamast, tehakse sellesse vastav kanne. </eesti>
<inglise>If the representative of the administrative offender refuses to sign the report, a corresponding note shall be made in the report. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja kirjalikud m&auml;rkused protokolli, samuti protokollile allakirjutamisest keeldumise kohta lisatakse protokollile. </eesti>
<inglise>The written statements of the representative of the administrative offender concerning the report and refusal to sign the report shall be appended to the report. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 39. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 39. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastutuse kohaldamine juriidilise isiku haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise asjas </eesti>
<inglise>Application of liability in matters concerning administrative offence of legal person </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Juriidilise isiku &otilde;iguserikkumise asja menetlus toimub haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus etten&auml;htud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Proceedings in matters concerning administrative offences of legal persons are conducted pursuant to the procedure prescribed in the Code of Administrative Offences. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel juriidilisele isikule m&auml;&auml;ratud rahatrahv n&otilde;utakse sisse haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus ja t&auml;itemenetluse seadustikus (RT I 1993, 49, 693; 1997, 43/44, 723; 1998, 41/42, 625; 51, 756; 61, 981; 103, 1695; 1999, 18, 302) kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Fines imposed on legal persons on the basis of this Act shall be collected pursuant to the procedure established by the Code of Administrative Offences and the Code of Enforcement Procedure (RT I 1993, 49, 693; 1997, 43/44, 723; 1998, 41/42, 625; 51, 756; 61, 981; 103, 1695; 1999, 18, 302). </inglise>
<eesti>5. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 5 </inglise>
<eesti>Rakenduss&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>Implementing Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 40. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 40. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude omanikele kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade v&auml;ljaandmine </eesti>
<inglise>Issue of cable television network licences to owners of cable television networks constructed prior to entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kohalike omavalitsuste korraldatud avalike konkursside tulemuste p&otilde;hjal s&otilde;lmitud lepingute alusel rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude omanike taotlusel v&auml;ljastab Sideamet neile kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu load kuue kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board shall issue cable television network licences to owners of cable television networks constructed under contracts entered into on the bases of the results of public competitions organised by local governments prior to the entry into force of this Act at the request of the owners within six months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba antakse v&auml;lja t&auml;htajaga k&uuml;mme aastat, kusjuures kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa tingimustes juhindutakse avaliku konkursi tulemuste p&otilde;hjal s&otilde;lmitud lepingus s&auml;testatud tingimustest, mis ei ole vastuolus seadusega. </eesti>
<inglise>Cable television network licences are issued for a term of ten years, whereas the conditions of a cable television network licence shall be based on the terms provided for in the contract entered into on the basis of the results of a public competition which are not in conflict with the law. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu lubade v&auml;ljaandmiseks k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 alusel peavad kohalikud omavalitsused kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates esitama Sideametile: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A local government shall, within three months after the entry into force of this Act, submit the following information to the Communications Board for the issue of cable television network licences pursuant to subsection (1) of this section: </inglise>
<eesti>1) avaliku konkursi tingimused; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the conditions of a public competition; </inglise>
<eesti>2) avaliku konkursi v&otilde;itnud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omaniku ja kohaliku omavalitsuse vahel s&otilde;lmitud lepingu koos kohaliku omavalitsuse koostatud &otilde;iendiga lepingu t&auml;itmise kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the contract entered into between the owner of a cable television network who won the public competition and the local government together with a certificate prepared by the local government confirming compliance with the contract; </inglise>
<eesti>3) muud dokumendid, mis t&otilde;endavad enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu rajamise &otilde;iguslikku alust. </eesti>
<inglise>3) other documents which prove the legal basis for the construction of the cable television network constructed prior to the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa saamiseks esitab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanik Sideametile vastavasisulise taotluse kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) To obtain a cable television network licence, the owner of a cable television network shall file an application to this effect with to the Communications Board within three months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba asendab Eesti Vabariigi sideseaduse (RT 1991, 3, 49) &sect; 7 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud riiklikku tegevuslitsentsi kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude osas. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A cable television network licence substitutes for a state activity licence for cable television networks specified in subsection 7 (2) of the Communications Act of the Republic of Estonia (RT 1991, 3, 49). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 41. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 41. </inglise>
<eesti>Ajutine t&auml;htajaline luba kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimise j&auml;tkamiseks </eesti>
<inglise>Temporary licence for specified term to continue operation of cable television network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude omanikele, kellele ei v&auml;ljastata kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 40 l&otilde;ike 1 alusel, v&auml;ljastatakse nende soovil ajutine t&auml;htajaline luba kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimise j&auml;tkamiseks kuni konkursi v&otilde;itja poolt rajatava kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimisele andmiseni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The owner of a cable television network constructed prior to the entry into force of this Act who is not issued a cable television network licence pursuant to subsection 40 (1) of this Act shall be issued a temporary licence for a specified term at the owner's request to continue the operation of the cable television network until the cable television network constructed by the winner of the competition is put into operation. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ajutise t&auml;htajalise loa saamiseks esitab kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanik kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates Sideametile vastavasisulise taotluse, millele lisatakse andmed abonentidega s&otilde;lmitud kehtivate lepingute kohta ja programmide edastamise &otilde;igust t&otilde;endavad dokumendid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) To obtain a temporary licence for a specified term, the owner of a cable television network shall file an application to this effect with the Communications Board within three months after the entry into force of this Act and shall append information concerning the valid contracts entered into with subscribers and documents which prove the right to transmit programmes. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideametil on &otilde;igus abonentide huvidest l&auml;htuvalt v&auml;ljastada ajutine t&auml;htajaline luba kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanikule, kelle tegevusluba on tunnistatud kehtetuks k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 22 l&otilde;ike 1 punktide 2, 3, 4 ja 8 alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Based on the interests of subscribers, the Communications Board has the right to issue a temporary licence for a specified term to the owner of a cable television network whose activity licence has been revoked pursuant to clauses 22 (1) 2), 3), 4) or 8) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Ajutine t&auml;htajaline luba annab &otilde;iguse kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimise j&auml;tkamiseks kuni konkursi v&otilde;itja poolt rajatava kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimisele andmiseni. </eesti>
<inglise>A temporary licence for a specified term entitles the owner to continue the operation of the cable television network until a cable television network constructed by the winner of the competition is put into operation. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui konkursi korraldaja pikendab konkursi v&otilde;istlust&ouml;&ouml;de esitamise t&auml;htaega k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 13 l&otilde;ike 2 punkti 6 alusel ning konkursi v&otilde;itjale v&auml;ljastatakse kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba p&auml;rast selles kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumist, v&auml;ljastab Sideamet kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omaniku soovil ajutise t&auml;htajalise loa kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimise j&auml;tkamiseks kuni konkursi v&otilde;itja poolt rajatava kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu opereerimisele andmiseni. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If the organiser of a competition extends the term for submission of competition projects pursuant to clause 13 (2) 6) of this Act, and the winner of the competition is issued a cable television network licence after expiry of the cable television network licence for the cable television network area, the Communications Board shall issue a temporary licence for a specified term to the owner of the cable television network at the latter's request to continue the operation of the cable television network until the cable television network constructed by the winner of the competition is put into operation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 42. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 42. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist rajatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemidele kasutuslubade v&auml;ljaandmine </eesti>
<inglise>Issue of utilisation licences for master antenna systems constructed prior to entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist rajatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steeme v&otilde;ib opereerida ilma kasutusloata kuni Sideamet v&auml;ljastab &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemide omanike taotlusel kasutusload k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 27 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Master antenna systems constructed prior to the entry into force of this Act may be operated without a utilisation licence until the Communications Board issues utilisation licences at the request of the owners of the master antenna systems pursuant to the procedure provided for in subsection 27 (2) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kasutusloa saamiseks esitab &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanik hiljemalt 2000. aasta 1. jaanuariks Sideametile vastavasisulise taotluse ja &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi projekti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) To obtain a utilisation licence, the owner of a master antenna system shall file an application to this effect and a design of the master antenna system with the Communications Board not later than 1 January 2000. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 43. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 43. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude rajamiseks tehtud kulutuste kompenseerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Reimbursement of expenses incurred in construction of cable television networks constructed prior to entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa konkursil osaleja ja konkursi v&otilde;itja v&otilde;i kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu omanik, kellele v&auml;ljastatakse kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 40 s&auml;testatud korras, on kohustatud samas kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rkude omaniku soovil ostma temalt kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kokkuleppehinnaga. </eesti>
<inglise>A participant in a competition for a cable television network licence who won the competition or the owner of a cable television network to whom a cable television network licence is issued pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect; 40 of this Act is required to purchase a cable television network constructed on a legal basis within the same cable television network area prior to the entry into force of this Act, at the request of the owner of the cable television network at an agreed price. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui kokkulepet ei saavutata, m&auml;&auml;rab hinna suuruse kohus, l&auml;htudes ostu-m&uuml;&uuml;gi objekti harilikust v&auml;&auml;rtusest. </eesti>
<inglise>Failing agreement, the price shall be determined by a court on the basis of the usual value of the object of purchase and sale. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 44. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 44. </inglise>
<eesti>Seadustes tehtavad muudatused ja t&auml;iendused </eesti>
<inglise>Amendments to Acts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Riigil&otilde;ivuseaduses (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 86, 1461; 87, 1466 ja 1467; 93, 1563; 1998, 2, 47; 4, 63; 23, 321; 36/37, 552 ja 553; 52/53, 771; 57, 859; 59, 941; 60, 951; 61, 979 ja 985; 64/65, 1004, 1005 ja 1008; 86/87, 1408; 97, 1519; 103, 1701; 108/109, 1783; 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 275) tehakse j&auml;rgmised t&auml;iendused: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 86, 1461; 87, 1466 and 1467; 93, 1563; 1998, 2, 47; 4, 63; 23, 321; 36/37, 552 and 553; 52/53, 771; 57, 859; 59, 941; 60, 951; 61, 979 and 985; 64/65, 1004, 1005 and 1008; 86/87, 1408; 97, 1519; 103, 1701; 108/109, 1783; 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 275) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 183 t&auml;iendatakse l&otilde;igetega 3 (4) kuni 3 (7) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>1) subsections (3 (4)) -(3 (7)) are added to &sect; 183 worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(3 (4)) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 1000 krooni + 10 krooni iga kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonna potentsiaalse abonendi kohta, kuid mitte &uuml;le 150 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>"(3 (4)) A state fee of 1000 kroons, plus 10 kroons per each potential subscriber within the cable television network area, but not more than 150 000 kroons shall be paid for the issue of a cable television network licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(3 (5)) Kaabeltelevisiooni kasutusloa v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 10 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(3 (5)) A state fee of 10 000 kroons shall be paid for the issue of a cable television network utilisation licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(3 (6)) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutusloa v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 1000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(3 (6)) A state fee of 1000 kroons shall be paid for the issue of a master antenna system utilisation licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(3 (7)) Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa pikendamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu pool esialgse loa riigil&otilde;ivu m&auml;&auml;rast. </eesti>
<inglise>(3 (7)) A state fee in the amount of one half of the amount of the state fee paid for the issue of the initial licence shall be paid for the extension of a cable television network licence. </inglise>
<eesti>&ldquo;; </eesti>
<inglise>&ldquo;; </inglise>
<eesti>2) seadust t&auml;iendatakse paragrahviga 197 (3) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) section 197 (3) is added to the Act worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 197 <hi rend="sup"> 3. </hi> Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa v&auml;ljaandmiseks korraldatavale konkursile osalejaks registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 197 (3). Registration as participant in competition organised for issue of cable television network licence </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa v&auml;ljaandmiseks korraldatavale konkursile osalejaks registreerimise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 1000 krooni + 10 krooni iga kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas asuva potentsiaalse abonendi kohta, kuid mitte &uuml;le 50 000 krooni." </eesti>
<inglise>A state fee of 1000 kroons, plus 10 kroons per each potential subscriber located within the cable television network area, but not more than 50 000 kroons shall be paid for registration as participant in a competition organised for the issue of cable television network licences." </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ringh&auml;&auml;linguseaduses (RT I 1994, 42, 680; 66, 1145; 1995, 83, 1437; 97, 1664; 1996, 49, 953; 1997, 29, 448; 52, 834; 93, 1564; 1998, 2, 42 ja 44; 1999, 16, 268) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused ja t&auml;iendused: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Broadcasting Act (RT I 1994, 42, 680; 66, 1145; 1995, 83, 1437; 97, 1664; 1996, 49, 953; 1997, 29, 448; 52, 834; 93, 1564; 1998, 2, 42 and 44; 1999, 16, 268) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 2 l&otilde;ikes 1 asendatakse s&otilde;nad "(saatjate ja saatjate v&otilde;rkudega)" s&otilde;nadega "(saatjate, saatjate v&otilde;rkude ja kaabelleviv&otilde;rkudega)"; </eesti>
<inglise>1) in subsection 2 (1), the words "(transmitters and networks of transmitters)" are substituted by the words "(transmitters, networks of transmitters and cable networks)"; </inglise>
<eesti>2) paragrahvi 37 l&otilde;ikes 3 asendatakse s&otilde;na "viit" s&otilde;naga "kuut" ja l&otilde;iget t&auml;iendatakse punktiga 6 j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>2) in subsection 37 (3), the word "five" is substituted by the word "six", and clause 6) is added to the subsection worded as follows: </inglise>
